title: Bug 49235 - ServletContainerInitializer onStartup(ClassSet is not expected
description: Bug 49235 - ServletContainerInitializer onStartup(Set<Class<? - The output is "MySomeClass". However, according to Servlet 3.0 spec, it is not yet implemented. My code works fine on Glassfish 3.0.
EB: I expect the output to be "MySomeClass".
SR: To reproduce the bug: 1. Run the code on a server that supports Servlet 3.0. 2. Observe the output, which should be "MySomeClass".
